        then (f.(p*s+(1-p)*t)-f.t)*(s-(p*s+(1-p)*t))
        <= (f.s-f.(p*s+(1-p)*t))*((p*s+(1-p)*t)-t) by A26,A29,REAL_2:185;
        then (f.(p*s+(1-p)*t)-f.t)*(s-t)*(1-p)
